ny cartoon.\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f311\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 CRAZY MIKE\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f311\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 More like quadruple crossed him.\par Trying to play both sides of the\par Masons and the Odd Fellows, Big Andy McRoy accused John Shatfield of treason before a tribunal held at the Northwest Regional Odd Fellow's picnic and gunny sack race.\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f311\fs24\sl220\s8\fi0\ri1440\li2160 ANGLE ON WINDOWS\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb240\f311\fs24\sl220\s3\fi0\ri1440\li2160 Mingo regains his footing and peers through the window in the background.\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f311\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 CRAZY MIKE (O/S) (cont'd)\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f311\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 Finding my great-great grandfather\par guilty on all charges, the Odd Fellows placed a curse on my family, leaving the remaining Shatfield generations without the use of our legs.\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb240\f311\fs24\sl220\s3\fi0\ri1440\li2160 Crazy Mike sadly looks down at his legs.\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f311\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 CRAZY MIKE (cont'd)\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f311\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 That night, during the weekly lodge\par meeting, my great-great grandfather\par fell to the ground in excruciating\par phantom pain. The Mason's tried to\par rebuke the curse of the Odd Fellow's, creating a catastrophic event indeed. A spiritual explosion...\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f311\fs24\sl220\s8\fi0\ri1440\li2160 INSERT - EXPLOSION\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb240\f311\fs24\sl220\s3\fi0\ri1440\li2160 RESUME\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f311\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 CRAZY MIKE (cont'd)\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f311\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 ...occurred, blocking anyone from entering the Secret Road to China until the two nemesis groups made peace with each other.\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f311\fs24\sl220\s4\f